        "content": "\n<font color=\"#5794f2\">\n<blockquote style=\"margin-top: 0px\">\n  <h1><b>Welcome to Netsage - TACC</b></h1>\n</font>\nNetSage is an open privacy-aware network measurement, analysis, and visualization service designed to provide near real-time monitoring and visualization of R&E data transfers. \nNetSage provides human-readable visualizations of normally opaque network data, helping ensure that scientific workflows are operating at maximum efficiency. \nNetSage services provide a combination of measurements, including SNMP and flow data, offering longitudinal network performance data visualization.\n<br>\n<br>\nSelect one of the questions below to begin exploring!\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
