        "content": "\u003cdiv class=\"netsage-banner\"\u003e\n  \u003ctable class=\"netsage-nav\" style=\"width: 100%; border: none;\"\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFlow Data:\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e\u003ch2\u003eGlobus Data:\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\n        \u003cul\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/xk26IFhmk?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top sources/destinations of flows?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/QfzDJKhik?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top flows by organization?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/-l3_u8nWk?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat do individual flows between sites look like?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          <li><a class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/ff11awegnesqod?from=${__from}&to=${__to}\">What do SSH flows between sites look like?</a></li>\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/b35BWxAZz\"\u003eWho are the top talkers over time?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/fgrOzz_mk?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top flows by country?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/WNn1qyaiz?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top flows by science discipline?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/ie7TeomGz?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top flows by project?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/ufIS9W7Zk?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the usage patterns by science discipline?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/CJC1FFhmz?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the current flow data summary statistics?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\n      \u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\n        \u003cul\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/xk26IFhml?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top sources/destinations of Globus tasks?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/QfzDJKhil?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top Globus tasks by organization?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/-l3_u8nWl?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat do individual Globus tasks between sites look like?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/b35BWxAZa\"\u003eWhat are the top Globus endpoints over time?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/fgrOzz_ml?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top Globus tasks by country?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/WNn1qyaia?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top Globus tasks by science discipline?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/ie7TeomGa?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top Globus tasks by project?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/ufIS9W7Zl?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the Globus usage patterns by science discipline?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/CJC1FFhma?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the current Globus task summary statistics?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e         \n        \u003c/ul\u003e\n      \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/table\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"netsage-column\"\u003e\n\n    \n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cstyle\u003e\n  .netsage-banner {\n  background-color: #618ED0;\n  padding: 1rem 15rem;\n  }\n  a.netsage-button-q {\n  color: white;\n  background-color: #759FDD;\n  padding: 4px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  a.netsage-button-q:hover {\n  color: white;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav tr, .netsage-nav td, .netsage-nav th{\n  border: none !important;\n  background: none !important;\n  color: white;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav td {\n  vertical-align: top;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav th h2{\n  font-weight: 800;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav li {\n  margin-top: 4px;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  font-size: 14pt;\n  }\n\u003c/style\u003e",
